<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;    Here is a list of  INTERNATIONAL  stories that moved Thursday,
Jan. 6, through 2:30 a.m. today, on The N.Y. Times News Service.
 &HT;    The stories go backward to 6:30 a.m. the previous day. Included
is story number, keyword, wordage, time sent (Eastern), priority
code and category code.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    INTERNATIONAL
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A9111 BC-EXP-MIDEAST-TALKS-1STLD-WRITETHRU-NYT 466 00:12 U I
 &HT;    WITH CLINTON PRESENT, PACE OF ISRAEL-SYRIA TALKS IS SAID TO PICK
UP
 &HT;    
 &HT;    A9106 BC-MIDEAST-TALKS-1STLD-WRITETHRU-425&AMP;ADD-NYT 679 00:05 U I
