<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FOR U.S. TAXPAYER, PRICE OF PEACE IN MIDEAST AT $20 BILLION -
AND CLIMBING
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (k) Commentary categories.
