<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ADVISORY-KREMLIN-INDEPENDENT-LONDON-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: DID YOU SEE THESE YELTSIN-RESIGNATION STORIES?...  
 
