   DNA-FREED (Tyler, Texas) _ A man who has served 16 years in
prison for rape is freed based on the results of DNA tests. When he
was convicted, the technology to clear A.B. Butler Jr. of the crime
didn't exist. By EVAN MOORE.
</P>
