during a Dec. 26 game at Foxboro Stadium. Flutie can't remember
what he said when Wade Phillips told him he was being benched
before the Bills' 31-6 win over the Indianapolis Colts on Jan. 2.
But Flutie remembers the same thing happening with the Patriots 11
years ago. (Matthew J. Lee/The Boston Globe)
