 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``St. Francis was a saint; I'm just a humble mayor. I have no
interest in becoming a saint. I am trying to apply common sense and
pragmatism.''
</P>
<P>
   _GIORGIO BARTOLINI, on his order banning the feeding of pigeons
in Assisi.
</P>
